Code:

print("Check whether palindrome or not\n")
n=int(input("Enter a number:\n"))
original_num=n
rev_num=0
while n>0:
    rem=n%10
    rev_num=rev_num*10+rem
    n=n//10
print("Reverse num:",rev_num)
if(original_num==rev_num):
    print("It is a palindrome")
else:
    print("It is not a palindrome")
    
Output:

Check whether palindrome or not

Enter a number:
Reverse num: 12321
It is a palindrome

Check whether palindrome or not

Enter a number:
Reverse num: 52846
It is not a palindrome